rows.label: tlk70000131_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I saw smoke coming from the capital,
and big black shadows were flying
around...

rows.label: tlk70000131_03_msg0002
rows.name:
It was really scary. Is everything OK
now?

rows.label: tlk70000131_03_msg0003
rows.name:
It's gotta be OK, or else you wouldn't
be here. Right?

rows.label: tlk70000131_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I'm scared that Hyber Village is
gonna be attacked, too.
